name: DEPRESSION
description: This art came out from the idea of raising mental health awareness. As individuals we all experience depressions in life and the knife piercing through signifies the feeling of a tortured mind. The bloody tears signifies the intensity of the emotion that the depress individual is feeling. And the Blue color symbolizes both sadness and serenity. With this Art that I made I hope that each one of us would have the genuine feeling of concern to each and everyone that we encounter.
